---
title: Pork Dumplings with Quick Pickled Veggie Salad and Soy Dipping Sauce
description: Making homemade dumplings sounds daunting, but we promise it’s way easier than you think! So put down that takeout menu and feast on our juicy dumplings, crunchy salad, and tangy soy sauce instead.
